    "Whisper models can be downloaded from HuggingFace (ggerganov/whisper.cpp).\nRecommended: ggml-tiny.en.bin or ggml-base.en.bin for real-time use.\n\nTo integrate whisper.cpp: add package https://github.com/ggerganov/whisper.cpp in Xcode → File → Add Package Dependencies." : {
