            "value" : "Whisper 模型可从 HuggingFace (ggerganov/whisper.cpp) 下载。\n推荐用于实时场景：ggml-tiny.en.bin 或 ggml-base.en.bin。\n\n集成 whisper.cpp：在 Xcode → File → Add Package Dependencies 中添加 https://github.com/ggerganov/whisper.cpp。"
